Text:
A huge THANK YOU for this rarity!!

Now almost all Beck movies are available - if only anyone could find the English language version of "Mannen som gick upp i rök"  http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0081117/ (yes it was shown in English in Sweden, with some of the characters dubbed, but that still has to be the most original version).
The last Beck,  “Mannen som gick upp i Rok“, is available from the Royal Swedish Library, but only for a Swedish student in the framework of some study....so.....you Sweeds, you can do it, I guess!
Thanks a lot! This is really a good movie. I can recommend it.
